Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:07.13,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
